verbose_text: However, immunoblotting using a polyclonal antibody raised against aa 201-421 of CEP104 detected two bands in a total cell lysate of this clone--a faint band at approximately 100 kDa and a more prominent band at 81 kDa, both displaying a strong reduction in expression compared to CEP104 levels in the parental hTERT-RPE1 wild-type (WT) cells (XREF_FIG B).
